r></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 12 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> Nvidia GeForce RTX 3050 or above<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 4 GB 可用空間</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": [], "developers": ["PantyParrot"], "publishers": ["Mango Party", "PantyParrot", "Mango Party News"], "price_overview": {"currency": "TWD", "initial": 32900, "final": 29600, "discount_percent": 10, "initial_formatted": "NT$ 329", "final_formatted": "NT$ 296"}, "categories": [{"id": 2, "description": "單人"}, {"id": 22, "description": "Steam 成就"}, {"id": 13, "description": "有字幕"}, {"id": 30, "description": "Steam 工作坊"}, {"id": 23, "description": "Steam 雲端"}, {"id": 62, "description": "親友同享"}], "genres": [{"id": "25", "description": "冒險"}, {"id": "4", "description": "休閒"}, {"id": "23", "description": "獨立製作"}, {"id": "28", "description": "模擬"}], "release_date": {"coming_soon": false, "date": "2024 年 12 月 12 日"}}}}, "us": {"2289720": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Kaiju Princess 2", "steam_appid": 2289720, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "dlc": [4093480, 3350770, 3350470], "detailed_description": "<h1>💟Add in WishList!!💟</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289720/extras/fef47b3544ea9f096a82f835fcf568e4.avif?t=1766072008\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are cosmic mercenary and a chef from Earth whose life goal is to create the ultimate culinary experience. Unfortunately, you are also on the run from the galactic police after a former companion betrayed and framed you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During a close shave with the authorities, you are saved by a literal monster. To your surprise, the monster turns into a beautiful pink-haired girl who claims to have sought you out for your cooking! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She (forcefully) offers to serve as your bodyguard in exchange for a place to live and a chance to try your delicious cooking every day.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Her crushing insistence and overwhelming power make it nigh impossible for you to refuse, so now you have to live together with this kaiju girl you just met!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289720/extras/675ad0f9e9adfea8798cde0881c91c4f.poster.avif?t=1766072008\" width=624 height=387 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289720/extras/675ad0f9e9adfea8798cde0881c91c4f.webm?t=1766072008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >💟Gameplay💟</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a journey to prove your innocence and complete your ultimate menu with a literal kaiju at your side!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collaborate to explore planets and collect ingredients while keeping the police off your tail! Study these exotic extraterrestrial ingredients and turn them into palatable dishes to satisfy the kaiju's need for &quot;earthling delicacies&quot;!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289720/extras/dda29fe871fe9c3c63757089d6da749d.avif?t=1766072008\" width=620 height=1100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She might be powerful, but she gets incredibly ravenous every time she uses her powers so you better get cooking and manage her appetite!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact with your cute kaiju companion and form a connection with her. There might be more to her than meets the eye...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289720/extras/5a5064cca1719a59d0cc119c70329ab3.poster.avif?t=1766072008\" width=683 height=433 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289720/extras/5a5064cca1719a59d0cc119c70329ab3.webm?t=1766072008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >💟Features💟</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immersive management-style game mechanics</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A fun, light-novel-style story experience</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple different outfits to earn, buy and swap</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect unique recipes that make you stronger</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leap across the stars with our planetary exporation system</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Larger-than-life tokusatsu-style boss battles</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgraded H-scenes, with additional exciting positions</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Takes place in the same universe as the original 《Kaiju Princess》</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289720/extras/1f92a3d0e5f67859f3cfac3bc8d6a768.poster.avif?t=1766072008\" width=645 height=478 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289720/extras/1f92a3d0e5f67859f3cfac3bc8d6a768.webm?t=1766072008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289720/extras/781d5fdca8f2ce3adfa9e05d3c4e6be8.poster.avif?t=1766072008\" width=614 height=896 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289720/extras/781d5fdca8f2ce3adfa9e05d3c4e6be8.webm?t=1766072008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >💟Characters💟</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289720/extras/0dd3781723b5688e306e30a7014a317c.avif?t=1766072008\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289720/extras_big/0dd3781723b5688e306e30a7014a317c.avif?t=1766072008 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289720/extras/75f21a3d3651c9fce704d667a05c3746.avif?t=1766072008\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289720/extras_big/75f21a3d3651c9fce704d667a05c3746.avif?t=1766072008 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289720/extras/1b09ed591003884e9fcd0cc3db6bf09a.avif?t=1766072008\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289720/extras_big/1b09ed591003884e9fcd0cc3db6bf09a.avif?t=1766072008 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289720/extras/3f0646fc72c08f638ff6975cfe9b15a2.avif?t=1766072008\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289720/extras_big/3f0646f